                            <item name="Description" type_name="gh_string" type_code="10">A number for the initial water content ratio [kg/kg]
_
The initial water content is assumed to be distributed evenly through
the depth of the material. UNITS ARE IN KG OF WATER PER KG OF DRY MATERIAL. (Default: 0)</item>
